  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  symptomatic complaints suggestive of preterm labor

          -  greater than 6 contractions per hour

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  multiple gestation

          -  rupture of amniotic membranes

          -  chorioamnionitis

          -  congenital malformations

          -  persistent vaginal bleeding

          -  abruptio placentae

          -  placenta previa

          -  previously diagnosed short cervix &lt; 2.5 cm

          -  cervical dilation &gt; 3 cm

          -  cervical cerclage

          -  exposure to tocolytic drugs

          -  allergy or contraindication to nifedipine
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
